000002  *>****************************************************************
000003  *>               Print one 940 Form on plain paper               *
000004  *>                                                               *
000005  *>     This program computes RI - Rhode Island tax at section    *
000006  *>      19 of the report - Should it not be in their State tax   *
000007  *>       table  instead ?                                        *
000008  *>      If so see code at                                        *
000009  *>    RD - "19 Rhode Island Portion of 15c                       *
000010  *>   and   code at arounbd 608 starting with :                   *
000011  *>      if       PY-PR1-Co-State = "RI"                          *
000012  *>                 move     WS-Tot-Taxable-Futa to WS-RI-Tax     *
000013  *>      etc.                                                     *
000014  *>                                                               *
000015  *>   Temp program name may be py210 - coding from print940       *
000016  *>                                                               *
000017  *>    Prograam uses RW - Report Writer.                          *
000018  *>                                                               *
000019  *>****************************************************************
000020  *>
000021   identification          division.
000022  *>================================
000023  *>
000024        program-id.       print940.
000025  *>**
000026        Author.           Vincent B Coen FBCS, FIDM, FIDPM, 08/03/2026.
000027  *>**
000028  *>    Security.         Copyright (C) 2025 - 2026 & later, Vincent Bryan Coen.
000029  *>                      Distributed under the GNU General Public License.
000030  *>                      See the file COPYING for details.
000031  *>**
000032  *>    Remarks.          Print Form 940 Report for end of year processing.
000033  *>                      Semi-sourced from Basic code from print940.
000034  *>**
000035  *>    Version.          See Prog-Name In Ws.
000036  *>**
000037  *>    Called Modules.   NONE other than SYSTEM to lpr.
000038  *>**
000039  *>    Functions Used:   NONE.
000040  *>
