000602                compute  WS-Tot-Tent-Cred =  WS-AddL-Credits + WS-Actual-Contrib
000603                compute  WS-Tot-Taxable-Futa = WS-Tot-Renum-Paid - WS-Exempt
000604                compute  WS-Gross-Fed-Tax = WS-Tot-Taxable-Futa * Ded-Co-Futa-Rate
000605                compute  WS-Maximum-Cred  = WS-Tot-Taxable-Futa * Ded-Co-Futa-Max-Credit
000606                if       WS-Tot-Tent-Cred < WS-Maximum-Cred
