000007C *> ** This copybook defines an EVALUATE statement capable of    **
000008C *> ** translating two-digit FILE-STATUS codes to a message.     **
000009C *> **                                                           **
000010C *> ** Use the REPLACING option to COPY to change the names of   **
000011C *> ** the MSG and STATUS identifiers to                         **
000012C *> ** the names your program needs.                             **
000013C *> Such as replacing STATUS by fs-reply msg by exception-msg.   **
000014C *>                                                              **
000015C *> ** chg 09/08/23 vbc for missing statuses                     **
